item.title: Github Page set Personal Website
item.description: GitHub Pages is a static site hosting service that hosts a person, organization, or project’s pages directly in a GitHub repository or repository. Hugo is a static site generator written in Go that is optimized for speed, ease of use, and configurability. It’s fast and flexible error I met *error: Source reference spec master does not match * error: Push some references to ‘github.com: ‘ solution: git commit -m "" You’ve added another git repository inside your current repository.
